ITPOINT&amp;&amp; 5124</span><span data-attr-index=\"2\">5120&amp;&amp;SPLITPOINT&amp;&amp; 5123</span></span><span>Versions: 2</span></div><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"><div><span>SMW Subobject for Freed</span><span>NPC location: South of the <a href=\"/w/Mind_Altar\" title=\"Mind Altar\">Mind Altar</a></span><span>Uses infobox: NPC</span><span>NPC ID: 5120,  5123</span><span>Examine: A dwarf.</span><span>Release date: 4 June 2007</span><span>Image: File:Rupert the Beard (freed).png</span><span>Is members only: true</span><span>Is variant of: Rupert the Beard</span></div><div><span>SMW Subobject for Captured</span><span>NPC location: South of the <a href=\"/w/Mind_Altar\" title=\"Mind Altar\">Mind Altar</a></span><span>Uses infobox: NPC</span><span>NPC ID: 5121,  5124</span><span>Examine: A dwarf. He seems to be in his underwear!</span><span>Release date: 4 June 2007</span><span>Image: File:Rupert the Beard.png</span><span>Is members only: true</span><span>Is variant of: Rupert the Beard</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Drain_pipe_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Drain pipe chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Drain_pipe_chathead.png?d2f64\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"65\" height=\"69\" data-file-width=\"65\" data-file-height=\"69\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Rupert_the_Beard_chathead.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rupert the Beard chathead.png\" src=\"/images/Rupert_the_Beard_chathead.png?a4f5e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"71\" height=\"120\" data-file-width=\"71\" data-file-height=\"120\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Rupert the Beard</b> is a friendly yet odd dwarf who speaks in a funny way, quite similar to <a href=\"/w/Sir_Tiffy_Cashien\" title=\"Sir Tiffy Cashien\">Sir Tiffy Cashien</a>, \"that namby pamby nincompoop\". When his good friend, Winkin the gnome farmer, was captured by <a href=\"/w/Nora_T._Hagg\" title=\"Nora T. Hagg\">Nora T. Hagg</a>, a notorious witch resident nearby <a href=\"/w/Taverley\" title=\"Taverley\">Taverley</a>, he went to rescue him but was captured and held in a tower by Princess <a href=\"/w/Miazrqa\" title=\"Miazrqa\">Miazrqa</a> of <a href=\"/w/Asgarnia\" title=\"Asgarnia\">Asgarnia</a>, who received a fake reason for the imprisonment from her second cousin twice removed Nora. While snooping in Nora's house, Rupert found a potion which he put into his <a href=\"/w/Dwarven_helmet\" title=\"Dwarven helmet\">helmet</a>, unbeknownst that it was a hair growth potion, which explains the length of his beard. During <a href=\"/w/Grim_Tales\" title=\"Grim Tales\">Grim Tales</a>, a <a href=\"/w/Miazrqa%27s_pendant\" title=\"Miazrqa&#39;s pendant\">lost pendant</a> is retrieved for the princess, who agrees to free Rupert. His armour has a special compartment to store his facial hair in.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stock\">Stock</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Rupert_the_Beard?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Stock\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Rupert_the_Beard?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Stock\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After freeing him, Rupert gives the player his helmet as a reward. If lost, a replacement can be obtained by paying Rupert 60,000 <a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\">coins</a>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; margin:0;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Item</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\">Price<br />sold at</th><th data-sort-type=\"number\"><a href=\"/w/Grand_Exchange\" title=\"Grand Exchange\">GE <br />price</a></th>\n</tr><tr style=\"text-align:center\"><td><a href=\"/w/Dwarven_helmet\" title=\"Dwarven helmet\"><img alt=\"Dwarven helmet.png\" src=\"/images/Dwarven_helmet.png?5eb13\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"26\" height=\"32\" data-file-width=\"26\" data-file-height=\"32\" /></a></td><td style=\"text-align:left\"><a href=\"/w/Dwarven_helmet\" title=\"Dwarven helmet\">Dwarven helmet</a></td><td data-sort-value=\"60000\"><a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\"><img alt=\"Coins 10000.png\" src=\"/images/Coins_10000.png?7fa38\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a> 60,000</td><td data-sort-value=\"49036\"><a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\"><img alt=\"Coins 10000.png\" src=\"/images/Coins_10000.png?7fa38\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a> 49,036</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Rupert_the_Beard?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Rupert_the_Beard?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Rupert's long beard is based upon the Grimm brothers' fairy tale of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rapunzel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Rapunzel\">Rapunzel</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Grim Tales\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Grim_Tales\" title=\"Template:Grim Tales\"><span title=\"View this templat